flowRoot.flowPara: The orange gradient represents motion. Animation and interactivity are an important part of bringing alive the user experience. In addition, the technology behind building sofware and the standards for design are never static. To continue creating a dynamic user experience requires a growth mentality that things outside the box (the orange square is moving out of the other two boxes) and one must constantly looking towards the bleeding edge of what is possible.
